snippet.title: BlackShot: Revolution Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
BlackShot: Revolution is a modernized systemic overhaul of the classic BlackShot experience. Featuring a fresh new look, revamped weapon balances and entirely cosmetic unique in-game purchases, Revolution emphasizes play-to-win, rather than the pay-to-win attitude often found in free-to-play games.

• Website: https://bs.sea.papayaplay.com/blackshotsea.do
• Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/blackshotsea/
• Discord: https://discord.gg/VY7DdeG
